divs: Sighting Detailswe were going to Ocala and I saw small red lights out my side window about 5 to 10 and a plane or chopper behind them as they went over us we could not see them after they pass over us there was no sound coming from the lights or the plane or chopper but there was a line coming off the plane or chopper we pulled off the road and watch the plane or chopper go away but could not see the lights. can you tell me what I saw. ufo or drones with a plane or chopper behind the lights? thanks
Summary: we were going to work, saw these lights passed over us and went on their way
